Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:31.81,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我和往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.64,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看准这个时间在这个道口等着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.91,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要问为什么 因为这里可以看到真岛的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.16,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很色气！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:42.98,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真岛正在看手机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:44.37,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不会注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:45.92,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,班里的小觉好像说过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:48.77,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真岛有个比她大的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.86,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,正在和男朋友聊天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:52.98,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:57.70,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是正在发「昨天的约会很开心呢」之类的消息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:00:59.50,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 真岛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:02.47,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会发一些更色情的大人之间的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.82,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「昨晚是个很棒的夜晚 谢谢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.18,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒的夜晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:09.59,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…晚上和男朋友做很棒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.42,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好色情 太色情了真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.05,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有些不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.46,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不甘心是什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:18.42,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真岛对我来说可望不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:20.90,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底像我这种栗子一样的光头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:22.24,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全配不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:24.43,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至看身高都配不上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:27.23,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 观赏真岛色气的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:30.27,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个身高非常有利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:32.89,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上高个子的家伙们 活该！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:35.82,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,手机那边正在聊天的混账男朋友 活该！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:39.29,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看到你所不知道的角度的真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:41.92,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:44.15,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.24,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真岛看着手机说了句「可恶」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.83,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这个气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:51.79,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真岛生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.17,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得 这个气氛下的真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:56.26,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也很色气！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:59.51,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被这个气氛下的真岛痛骂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:02.57,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我一边下跪都可能会兴奋！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.70,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个暂且不说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.57,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真岛和手机那边聊天的男朋友发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:13.12,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「虽然昨晚很棒 从今晚开始走夜路要注意哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:16.47,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友 真活该 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:20.77,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我刚刚因别人的吵架而高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:21.89,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为别人的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.47,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是因真岛的不幸而高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:26.88,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这种行为不符合我做人的准则
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.68,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,得向真岛道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:29.66,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必须道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.68,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 突然被人道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.89,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会莫名其妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.89,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我就对着真岛的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.90,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,默默地低下头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.01,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我做人的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:41.90,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉 真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:42.93,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.68,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:47.82,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.42,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,从道歉这个角度抬头看真岛的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:52.92,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比以往…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.36,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,更加色气！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.58,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是罪孽深重！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.62,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:00.40,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太罪孽深重了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.43,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必须再次道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.21,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必须向真岛道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.43,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事必须下跪才能表达歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:09.82,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但…跪下的角度看真岛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.44,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会是怎样的风景？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.44,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.17,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在想什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:19.67,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是田西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.28,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
